1601179200.title: Managing Asia
1601179200.descr: Managing Asia is a series of in-depth conversations with some of the most influential business leaders in Asia today, who are changing the business landscape on the continent. Join host Christine Tan, as she interviews CEOs and entrepreneurs about various issues, as well as their professional inspirations and goals.

1601181000.title: CNBC Meets
1601181000.descr: Tania Bryer sits down with some of the most powerful and recognisable names in the world. Featuring guests from a diverse range of industries, Tania discusses both their professional and personal lives, revealing the people behind the names. Whether from the worlds of business, sport, entertainment or politics, the guests reveal the highs and lows of their respective careers, also expanding on their philanthropic ventures.

1601182800.title: American Greed: Fools Gold
1601182800.descr: American Greed is a documentary series focussing on the largest white-collar crimes, also known as financial or corporate crimes, throughout the history of America. We explore the lengths these opportunistic scam artists go to for their own personal gain. The masterminds behind theses flawed plans certainly learn one thing; crime doesn't pay. Narrated by American actor Stacy Keach.

1601186400.title: Joel Osteen: Jo855 – Calling Over Comfort
1601186400.descr: Hear the messages of hope that best-selling author, evangelist and the senior pastor of Lakewood Church, Joel Osteen is delivering in each episode. Joel's positive and encouraging speeches will allow viewers to hear God's message of hope, love and victory and be inspired to do great things in life.

1601188200.title: Answers With Bayless Conley (f)
1601188200.descr: In this religious television show Pastor Bayless Conley of the Cottonwood Christian Center, explains how religion can be used as a solution for various issues. Join him as he talks about the practical teachings of the Bible, while addressing serious problems, including depression and addiction.

1601190000.title: In Touch Ministries
1601190000.descr: In Touch Ministries is a long-running television series in which senior pastor of the First Baptist Church in Atlanta, Dr Charles Stanley, shares lessons about the Christian faith. He discusses various themes, such as family, prayer, motherhood and fear, addressing stories from the Bible and offering a deeper understanding of Christian teachings.

1601191800.title: New Creation Church With Joseph Prince: Speak Out What You Believe In Christ!
1601191800.descr: Religious programme with spiritual messages on life and faith, religious interpretations and words of praise and worship. Hosted by Joseph Prince, the senior pastor and co-founder of the New Creation Church in Singapore – a large non-denominational Christian church in Asia. With his energetic and sometimes humorous style, Joseph Prince has spoken to live audiences across the world and his sermons are broadcast globally.
